text: Paweł Kaczmarek (born 8 September 1995) is a Polish sprint kayaker. He competed in the K-1 200 m event at the 2016 Summer Olympics, but failed to reach the final. In 2015 he was named Athlete of the Year of the Lubusz Voivodeship. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Canoeists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic canoeists of Poland Category:Polish male canoeists Category:People from Człuchów Category:European Games competitors for Poland Category:Canoeists at the 2015 European Games Category:Canoeists at the 2019 European Games
